    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>You attended an event. Write an article for your blog.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Yesterday, I attended at the launch of the new perfume of the Delavigne corporation, the famous Californian's firm.</p>
                <p>Everybody received a sample of it. More than hundred people attended the event and the flagrances that diffused hundred bottles of the perfume was wonderful.</p>
                <p>The Parisian's perfumers can have a big problem with this American' competition.</p>
                <p>France is no more the best in this matter.</p>
                <p>This new perfume is called &quot;blue moon&quot;, and it's certainly will become a great succes, not only because it's splendid flagrance but shurely with the skilled marketing of the Americans.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment">A2? Vocab, logic B1-B2; wrong word order A2.</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment">Weak B1.</note>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </body>
